INSERT INTO `wp_em_events` VALUES (1,75,'bill-nye-vs-ken-ham-debate-watch',2,1,'Bill Nye vs. Ken Ham Debate Watch','18:00:00','20:30:00',0,'2014-02-04','2014-02-04','Join Secular Students at Iowa and help cheer on your favorite television scientist on February 4th!',0,NULL,'00:00:00',NULL,0,0,4,NULL,NULL,'a:0:{}','2014-01-24 03:48:26','2014-02-03 05:00:37',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,0),(2,235,'secsi-general-meeting',3,1,'SecSI General Meeting','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-02-18','2014-03-11',NULL,0,NULL,'00:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,NULL,NULL,'a:0:{}','2014-02-03 05:05:38',NULL,1,1,'weekly','2',1,0,NULL,0),(3,237,'secsi-general-meeting-2014-02-18',3,1,'Darwin Day Presentation','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-02-18','2014-02-18','SecSI will be meeting to discuss Charles Darwin, his life, and his contributions to the field of biology. We will also talk about John Logsdon\'s upcoming lecture.\r\n\r\nAfter the meeting, we will attend a gathering of Unitarian Universalist Secular Humanists.',0,'2014-02-18','00:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2014-02-03 05:05:38','2014-02-17 19:32:10',0,1,'weekly','2',1,0,NULL,0),(4,238,'secsi-general-meeting-2014-02-25',3,1,'Sex, cells: Origins and Natural History of Meiosis','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-02-25','2014-02-25','John Logsdon, an associate professor of Biology, the director of the Pentacrest Museums, and Secular Students at Iowa\'s faculty advisor will give a lecture on February 25th. This event will be the culmination of our two week focus on Charles Darwin, and will occur after Iowa City\'s Darwin Day events from February 21st-23rd. His topic is his research on the evolution of sex.\r\n\r\nProfessor Logsdon\'s research focuses on understanding the molecular natural history of sexual reproduction, focusing specifically on meiosis, the special cell division that allows for sex to proceed. We are studying diverse biological systems that appear, in various ways, to be exceptions to many \"rules\" in sexual biology. Using data gathered from studies of these various organisms, we ask and attempt answer some of the following questions: When did sex and meiosis arise? How and from what prior function(s) did sex and Meiosis derive? How has sex subsequently evolved? Can sex and meiosis be lost? ',0,'2014-02-25','00:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,0,NULL,'a:0:{}','2014-02-03 05:05:38','2014-02-24 21:21:58',0,1,'weekly','2',1,0,NULL,0),(5,239,'secsi-general-meeting-2014-03-04',3,1,'SecSI General Meeting','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-03-04','2014-03-04',NULL,0,'2014-03-04','18:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,2,NULL,'N;','2014-02-03 05:05:38',NULL,0,1,'weekly','2',1,0,NULL,0),(6,240,'secsi-general-meeting-2014-03-11',3,1,'SecSI General Meeting','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-03-11','2014-03-11',NULL,0,'2014-03-11','18:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,2,NULL,'N;','2014-02-03 05:05:38',NULL,0,1,'weekly','2',1,0,NULL,0),(7,248,'walking-away',8,1,'\"Losing Our Religion\"','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-03-25','2014-03-25','How did you lose your faith? Why did you leave your religion? Why do you feel the need to be involved in a secular community? How can you live without religion in a highly-religious nation?\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOn March 25th, we will get together to discuss our transition to unbelief. Many of us were raised with religion, only to lose it as young adults. For most of us, this transition was neither easy nor painless. As we share our unique journeys, we can benefit from the experiences and ideas of our fellow secular students. Anyone who desires to share his or her story or hear from those who have had similar experiences is welcome to attend.',0,'2014-03-11','00:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,0,NULL,'a:1:{s:6:\"Layout\";s:4:\"2c-l\";}','2014-02-03 20:16:11','2014-03-18 14:46:46',0,1,'weekly','2',1,NULL,NULL,0),(8,249,'game-night',8,1,'Game Night','18:00:00','19:00:00',0,'2014-05-06','2014-05-06','Before the stress of exam week hits us all, SecSI will be meeting for a night of fun and games! For our final meeting of the semester, we will be relaxing, chatting, and playing Cards Against Humanity.',0,'2014-03-11','00:00:00',NULL,0,0,5,NULL,NULL,'a:0:{}','2014-02-03 20:22:01','2014-02-03 20:26:13',0,1,'weekly','2',1,NULL,NULL,0);
