 leave your religion? Why do you feel the need to be involved in a secular community? How can you live without religion in a highly-religious nation?\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOn March 25th, we will get together to discuss our transition to unbelief. Many of us were raised with religion, only to lose it as young adults. For most of us, this transition was neither easy nor painless. As we share our unique journeys, we can benefit from the experiences and ideas of our fellow secular students. Anyone who desires to share his or her story or hear from those who have had similar experiences is welcome to attend.','\"Losing Our Religion\"','','publish','open','closed','','walking-away','','','2014-03-18 14:46:46','2014-03-18 19:46:46','',0,'http://secularstudents.org.uiowa.edu/?post_type=event&#038;p=248',0,'event','',0),(249,8,'2014-02-03 20:25:41','2014-02-03 20:25:41','Before the stress of exam week hits us all, SecSI will be meeting for a night of fun and games! For our final meeting of the semester, we will be relaxing, chatting, and playing Cards Against Humanity.','Game Night','','publish','open','open','','game-night','','','2014-02-03 20:26:13','2014-02-03 20:26:13','',0,'http://secularstudents.org.uiowa.edu/?post_type=event&#038;p=249',0,'event','',28),(250,8,'2014-02-03 20:25:07','2014-02-03 20:25:07','','CAH','','inherit','open','open','','cah','','','2014-02-03 20:25:07','2014-02-03 20:25:07','',249,'http://secularstudents.org.uiowa.edu/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/CAH.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(251,2,'2014-02-04 01:54:19','2014-02-04 01:54:19','<p>Welcome to the <em>List of Resources for Doubters</em>, or LORD. Curated by Secular Students at Iowa, the LORD is comprised of media resources, such as online videos and websites, that embody themes of atheism, humanism, skepticism, the scientific method, and the amazing spectrum of topics that extend from there.</p><b>How it Works:</b>\r\n<p>The LORD is split into categories by media type, which you can see bel